FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1776172267
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died in
OL,4,Cstabbing as fundraisers set up
OL,6,FA separate fundraiser has been set up
OL,7,Fin his memory to raise money to
OL,8,Fsupport the Safer Kent charity which
OL,9,Fworks to help tackle and prevent crime.
OL,11,FA statement on the fundraising page
OL,12,Fsaid: "No family should have to feel
OL,13,Fthis pain.
OL,15,F"No mother or father should have to
OL,16,Fget that call or the knock at the door
OL,17,Fto tell them their child isn't coming
OL,18,Fhome.
OL,20,F"You never think it will happen to
OL,21,Fyou, til it does.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
